<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="vacation-n">vacation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /və'keɪʃn, veɪ'keɪʃn/    美 /veɪ'keɪʃn, və'keɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U] </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-bre-holiday">1.★ <strong>假期；休假 (BrE holiday)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>summer / Christmas vacation</strong>
暑假/圣诞假期</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="have-take-a-vacation">have / take a vacation</h3>
<p>1.<strong>休假：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The first thing I’m going to do is to take a long vacation! 
我要做的第一件事是休一个长假。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 2</footer></div>

<h3 id="on-vacation">on vacation</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在度假：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some people write postcards while they are on vacation and send them to friends. 
一些人在度假的时候写明信片并寄给朋友。</p><footer>2012 湖南改</footer></div></div>